1
00:01:09,080 --> 00:01:10,640
This company's database

2
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:12,360
isn't for just any nobody to access

3
00:01:13,800 --> 00:01:14,400
This security, huh,

4
00:01:14,520 --> 00:01:15,560
really needs an upgrade

5
00:01:16,040 --> 00:01:17,440
I'm Hong Ye's man

6
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:18,800
In Dongba,

7
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:20,640
anyone who goes against Hong Ye

8
00:01:21,040 --> 00:01:22,640
is asking to die

9
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:23,640
Are you done yet?

10
00:01:23,760 --> 00:01:24,600
What'd you say?

11
00:01:24,840 --> 00:01:25,200
Get him!

12
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,360
Rough him up first!

13
00:01:37,400 --> 00:01:38,200
Enough.

14
00:01:38,400 --> 00:01:39,360
You've beaten him enough.

15
00:01:39,880 --> 00:01:40,720
Take us inside.

16
00:01:43,520 --> 00:01:44,000
Ding Ding.

17
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,640
The password.

18
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:45,840
Sis,

19
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:48,480
there was never a password for the records room

20
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:50,280
Fu Qiang.

21
00:01:51,480 --> 00:01:53,200
If you're so capable, crack it yourselves!

22
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:54,000
It's fine.

23
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:55,600
I can crack it.

24
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:05,240
We've only got five minutes.

25
00:02:11,640 --> 00:02:13,000
It's already at 50 percent.

26
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:20,520
What's going on?

27
00:02:20,520 --> 00:02:22,400
It's a sudden external cyberattack.

28
00:02:29,440 --> 00:02:31,120
Only three minutes left!

29
00:02:31,240 --> 00:02:33,000
Don't think a few cheap tricks

30
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,280
means you can mess with high-tech.

31
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,800
Your system

32
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,280
is about to crash.

33
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,080
A Di!

34
00:02:38,440 --> 00:02:39,440
This computer lacks computing power.

35
00:02:39,440 --> 00:02:40,240
Get me another one.

36
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,120
What the hell.

37
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,160
You think adding a keyboard

38
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:46,480
will make it go faster?

39
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:47,680
What a joke.

40
00:02:49,640 --> 00:02:50,440
One minute!

41
00:02:50,680 --> 00:02:51,720
87 percent!

42
00:02:53,920 --> 00:02:54,760
30 seconds!

43
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,120
95 percent!

44
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,600
Ding Ding!

45
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:13,520
Where's the cloud PC called Little Nest?

46
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,440
We were short on time and under pressure,

47
00:03:15,600 --> 00:03:17,040
so I couldn't disable the wipe system.

48
00:03:17,280 --> 00:03:17,880
So I

49
00:03:17,880 --> 00:03:18,520
synced the data

50
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,040
to that computer instead.

51
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,800
Found it.

52
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,400
It's here.

53
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:30,880
No way.

54
00:03:31,040 --> 00:03:32,320
You're just a waiter.

55
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,640
That's impossible.

56
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:36,880
What?

57
00:03:37,080 --> 00:03:37,720
What are you doing?

58
00:03:39,120 --> 00:03:39,800
Don't come any closer!

59
00:03:55,040 --> 00:03:56,160
At least the data's safe.

60
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:57,800
Think about it carefully.

61
00:03:58,480 --> 00:03:59,880
It shouldn't be this simple.

62
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:26,200
Hello?

63
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:27,280
Sorry.

64
00:04:27,640 --> 00:04:29,680
Not killing you was my mistake.

65
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:30,800
Sorry to disappoint you.

66
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,280
Guess I'm just hard to kill.

67
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:33,880
I wanna ask you something.

68
00:04:34,800 --> 00:04:35,800
Why did you want me dead?

69
00:04:35,880 --> 00:04:36,600
A Di,

70
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,760
don't try to test me.

71
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:39,280
We'll meet again.

72
00:04:43,160 --> 00:04:44,240
The call was too short.

73
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,200
We can't trace it.

74
00:04:50,160 --> 00:04:51,360
Let's head back.

75
00:05:08,720 --> 00:05:09,480
This is bad!

76
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:11,040
Lao Zhang and Ding Ding are gone!

77
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:11,840
Gone?

78
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:17,920
Xingyu!

79
00:05:18,280 --> 00:05:20,520
Besides the company,

80
00:05:20,520 --> 00:05:21,680
where does Dr. Zhang usually like to go?

81
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,520
Sometimes he goes to the lab.

82
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,560
The lab.

83
00:05:27,720 --> 00:05:29,000
Then let's check the lab.

84
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,480
It's the lab's landline.

85
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:35,760
Let's go!

86
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,000
There are at least five of them.

87
00:05:53,360 --> 00:05:54,360
They're brutal.

88
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,120
Are they the same ones who blew up our car?

89
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:00,120
Hard to say.

90
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:03,720
Did Dr. Zhang piss someone off?

91
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:07,000
Dr. Zhang keeps a low profile.

92
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:09,280
We opened a branch here

93
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:11,440
to extract rare minerals.

94
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,040
Ms. Shen!

95
00:06:27,560 --> 00:06:28,480
You're finally here.

96
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:29,000
Lao Xue.

97
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:30,560
What the hell happened?

98
00:06:30,960 --> 00:06:32,000
I'm not totally sure either.

99
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,080
A group showed up

100
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,800
and took Professor Zhang.

101
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,000
Boss Ding Ding,

102
00:06:36,280 --> 00:06:36,840
look.

103
00:06:37,120 --> 00:06:38,360
She's been freaking out over there.

104
00:06:47,280 --> 00:06:48,160
Ding Ding!

105
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:52,680
Brother A Di!

106
00:06:55,880 --> 00:06:56,960
When I got here,

107
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:58,400
I didn't see Dr. Zhang.

108
00:06:58,680 --> 00:06:59,960
But I found his phone.

109
00:07:02,320 --> 00:07:03,480
Ms. Shen.

110
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:04,560
I'm fine.

111
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:06,600
They just asked me to come sit for a bit.

112
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:07,720
Lao Xue,

113
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,760
please take Youyou back first.

114
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:11,040
Alright.

115
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,960
Lao Zhang would never call me Ms. Shen.

116
00:07:20,160 --> 00:07:21,520
He said it on purpose.

117
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:22,720
He's been kidnapped.

118
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:25,000
Good thing I stuck around.

119
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,440
One net,

120
00:07:28,880 --> 00:07:30,080
two big fish.

121
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,280
How are you not dead?

122
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:39,880
That was just my double.

123
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:42,080
You think I'm that easy to kill?

124
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:42,640
A Di.

125
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:44,120
You think someone like you

126
00:07:44,400 --> 00:07:45,720
can kill me?

127
00:07:46,480 --> 00:07:47,160
First,

128
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:50,000
I wasn't the one who fired.

129
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,160
Second,

130
00:07:51,880 --> 00:07:53,240
I knew from the start

131
00:07:53,360 --> 00:07:54,960
the one who died was a double.

132
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:56,440
If I didn't play along,

133
00:07:56,880 --> 00:07:58,160
would you have shown up here?

134
00:07:58,880 --> 00:08:00,480
So the one standing in front of me now

135
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,600
must be the real General Dawa, huh?

136
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:04,440
If you die this time,

137
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,560
you'll be dead for real.

138
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:09,320
You set this up on purpose.

139
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:11,200
Where did you take Lao Zhang?

140
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:13,160
I'm not interested in him at all.

141
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,640
I'm only interested in you.

142
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:16,560
Come back with me.

143
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,320
I'll let everything slide.

144
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,200
She's not going with you.

145
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,320
I guess

146
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:37,640
you wouldn't dare shoot.

147
00:08:37,760 --> 00:08:39,480
I guess you guessed wrong

148
00:08:42,200 --> 00:08:43,280
Take a guess

149
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,800
if I dare to shoot.

150
00:08:48,120 --> 00:08:49,520
This is Dongba

151
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:51,040
If you dare to shoot,

152
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,920
Hong Ye won't spare you

153
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,360
you and your woman won't get out alive

154
00:08:55,960 --> 00:08:57,000
Stop!
